{"tid":855332,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大學無粗口讀","createTime":"2018-10-10T03:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T04:02:30.000Z","uid":204943,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae96a86f040947a484a4b6b94cb229cc241dda4b","tid":855332,"uid":204943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:50:27.000Z","msg":"粗口係香港傳統文化<br />\n極具影響力同推動力<br />\n例如碼頭咕哩講句屌那媽頂硬上<br />\n就可以充滿動力繼續工作<br />\n動力係生存之本<br />\n比歷史/科技更為重要<br />\n最重要係大家都讀得開心<br />\n做人都係想開心下姐<br />\n又有知識落袋又開心<br />\n何樂而不為<br />\n好過哂其他為讀而讀嘅GE科<br />\n粗口根本就係人際交往必修科<br />\n起身呀柒頭總是比good morning 更有誠意<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"957538987ebbc89142f788a365559f00ae995452","tid":855332,"uid":198622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bda2754572a304132da8c1374355ba3bbf145df8","tid":855332,"uid":21886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"點解大學無性交道部"},{"pid":"b103fbcf596a6d8fa34ddada32df92c055db44fa","tid":855332,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"八大都有喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔係八大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ba65a092cc7e4040cf8e8b65c43175e713ae96","tid":855332,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"好多嘢都重要㗎啦<br />\n個個都開一科點搞啊"},{"pid":"3561c9e1f93c6f343fa6b756fb0ac33c01e2a1ab","tid":855332,"uid":200975,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"粗口唔洗教個個都識啦<br />\n應該開啲科教班蝗正確咁屙屎屙尿 咁對香港仲有益"}]}